Story VHYEATqz5 AC-1

Implemented hosted cursor lifecycle primitives on the shared server protocol:
- OperationRequest and OperationResponse now carry create/get/advance/ack/delete cursor operations.
- RemoteClient exposes create_cursor, get_cursor, advance_cursor, ack_cursor, and delete_cursor.
- handle_request routes cursor operations to the existing LocalEngine cursor APIs.
- Server regression coverage exercises remote cursor create/get/ack/delete and not-found behavior.
